# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 11. UPDATING / DEPLOYING CHANGES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# After making changes locally:
#
# Deploy specific files:
#   scp server.mjs joseph_bridge.py root@srv1390882.hstgr.cloud:/root/fde/missioncanvas-site/
#
# Deploy workspace data:
#   scp workspaces/oil-investor/*.yaml root@srv1390882.hstgr.cloud:/root/fde/missioncanvas-site/workspaces/oil-investor/
#
# Restart after deploy:
#   ssh root@srv1390882.hstgr.cloud 'systemctl restart missioncanvas && sleep 2 && systemctl restart joseph-bridge mc-monitors'
#
# NOTE: Restarting mc-tunnel changes the URL! Only restart it if needed.
# If you must restart it, update the MCP config with the new URL.
